summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 6, Block 1, Byron Addition; Lots 3, 4 and 5, Block 1, Fern Hill Additions; and portion of Tract 24, Dunlap's Plat of Land on Lake Washington; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-297 and 17-242, respectively.
